✅Why do we pump on Hotbit?

Hotbit is the best exchange for pumps for several reasons. It allows users form anywhere in the world, its used by millions, and it offers a wide variety of coins. Buying/selling on Hotbit is done with limit orders, this is also optimal for pumps it will help keep the price as high as possible for as long as possible.
 
 ✅How to pump on Hotbit ?
 
1. Firstly, you will need an account on Hotbit. Register here https://hotbit.io/ We pump on Hotbit because it has the best environment for pumps, has protection for users, and it vastly used all across the world. 2.  ✅ How to trade?
 🟢To buy 🟢 Navigate to the coin market either using the url or search bar. Here is an example https://www.hotbit.io/exchange?symbol=ETH_USD

1.)After you are on the coin/usdt page click a RED order from the order book, the higher you click up the better the chance of completing the order. This will copy that orders price for you and auto fill it in. If you prefer, you can enter your own price manually (but this slows you down of course)

2) Click/slide the order amount to 100%, this will buy the coin with 100% of your balance, you can use any amount here: if you only want to spend 75% then click 75%, for example
3) Click "Buy" and your order will post. Because Hotbit uses only limit orders, setting your price higher than the current price will help make sure your order fills

🔴To Sell 🔴 When the coin has reached the "target gain" list a limit sell so your coins can sell, you can click a green order to prefill the price.
